      </mj-section>
      <mj-section>
        <mj-column>
          <mj-text
            font-size="32px"
            line-height="48px"
            font-weight="700"
            color="#000"
            text-transform="capitalize"
            padding-top="10px"
            font-family="Inter"
            align="center"
          >
            Account Disabled.
          </mj-text>
        </mj-column>
      </mj-section>
      <mj-section>
        <mj-column>
          <mj-text
            font-size="14px"
            line-height="21px"
            font-weight="400"
            color="#666"
            text-transform="capitalize"
            padding-top="0px"
            font-family="Inter"
            align="left"
          >
            Hey there {{firstName}}, <br />
            Your Xtride account has been disabled, because {{reason}}
            <br> If you think something is incorrect or if you need help, send an email to <a style="color:#000" href="mailto:support@xtridelink.com">support@xtridelink.com</a> and get in touch with our team. 
            <br>
            <br>
